# Local GnuPG homes and secret key stores
.gnupg/
gnupg-master/
**/.gnupg/
**/gnupg-master/
**/private-keys-v1.d/
**/secring.gpg
out/*

# Secret key exports generated by the helper scripts
**/master-secret-backup.asc
**/*-subkey.asc
**/*-subkey.b64

# Key generation batch files can embed passphrases
**/master-key.batch
